          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The nuclear  photoeffect  in  tritium induced by 32.5",
                " MeV bremsstrahlung  has  been  investigated.  Energy",
                " spectra  of protons and deuterons from the reactions",
                " H-3(g,p)2n  and  H-3(g,n)d were separately  recorded",
                " by  E-dE semiconductor telescope.  The cross section",
                " of the reaction H-3(g,n)D is given for Eg = 18 -  28",
                " MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
